post.description:
Verify Turnkey session and return JWT token

Request body:
{
    "token": "eyJ..."  (Turnkey session token)
}

Returns:
{
    "token": "eyJ...",  (Our JWT token, valid for 30 days)
    "expires_in": 2592000
}

The userId and organizationId are extracted from the Turnkey token payload.
